DTSTAMP:20260322T052744Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260327T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260328T001500
SUMMARY:(H.B.G.) - Harrisburg Board Gaming
DESCRIPTION:Central PA Game Club\nCome to game night in the Harrisburg are
 a! Every 2nd and 4th Friday of every month\, there will be gaming at the L
 ife Point Church. Event starts at 6:00pm in the Churches Lobby / Sitting A
 rea and goes until you're too tired to play anymore. You can come anytime 
 and leave anytime. Keep in mind you might have to wait to get into a game 
 if you come later depending on games being played. Or if you come with fam
 ily or a friend group\, a game can be provided by the event for you to pla
 y when you arrive!\n\nSome Snacks and Drinks are provided (but not guarant
 eed for each event). Feel Free to bring your own games\, food and drinks! 
 We have a kitchen available to be used with a Microwave and a Fridge for y
 our drinks. Come check us out!\n\nJon Krehling is the organizer of this ev
 ent\, so message him on meetup if you have any questions!
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/centralpagameclub/events/308160860/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20250530T160137Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20250530T160137Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Central PA Game Club
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/centralpagameclub/
